title: Taylor's Spooky Lyrics
description:
It's spooky szn and our girl Taylor Swift likes to use some haunting imagery in her songs! Here are just some of the ones that felt festive, because 'tis the damn season!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us next? There are lots of ways to reach us!
